Building an AI Dietician with Python is entirely achievable using an LLM API (like OpenAI's GPT-4o or Google's Gemini) for the NLP engine, paired with Streamlit or FastAPI for the frontend and routing. [1]
This comprehensive, step-by-step blueprint outlines how to structure the application using Python and key libraries.
1. Project Architecture & Core Libraries
